"Entering <userinput><command>file:/directoryname</command></userinput> in "
"&konqueror; lists the files of this folder."
msgstr ""
"Vnos <userinput><command>file:/ime_imenika</command></userinput> v "
"&konqueror;-ju izpiše datoteke v tem imeniku."

